cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SD

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about multilingual natural language processing and language models. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a neural language model to learn continuous vector representations of language. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving inference about language varieties not seen during training. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper proposes a character-based neural language model. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is a less likely category as the paper does not seem to be directly related to sound processing, but it is still a possibility as the paper deals with language and its representations.
